{
  "stem": "21786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I walked around the washing facilities, being, I mean, having the band on my arm and similar, and reporting to Mengele every day personally, so I had the privileged position that I could move wherever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there behind the block, in the spring suddenly, I have seen a small tree growing up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the tree had green leaves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It sounds idiotic, but somehow, looking at the tree, I had a notion, if this tree can survive, so can you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If this tree made it, maybe you'll make it, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was one of these things-- that was the only thing which was growing there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in the position as I was, every day I reported to the SS man who was on duty for-- there were so-called sick people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a conglomerate of diseases starting for us-- pneumonia, ending with typhus, and typhoid fever, and special dysentery which, I think, they spread among us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was, what I found out many, many years later, a dysentery called Shiga-Kruse-- which was prevalent-- which is prevalent in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They're testing it for the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And people are dying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And people were lying there every morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my duty was to also write the death certificate for these dead people, for they had to be taken away, taken off the central registry.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so I had to take the tattoo number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was written on a special form.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There were two diagnoses-- ONE diagnosis was pneumonia, THE other one was weakness of the heart.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was up to my choice, simply, what I put there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had to sign it, 10065765.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I-- many, many times a day I was signing this thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
